column106: I think the system has difficulties with reading ( and ), it sometimes mixes up which sub part belongs to which side of the operators. The system performs sufficiently well for non-combined logic formulas. For example, starting with one E or A and limited or/and connections. The systems appears to me as if it is able to structurally read the logic formulas which is a nice thing.
